column2: Do you experience any difficulties in managing your weight?
Do you believe your current diet provides all the necessary nutrients?
How often do you eat fruits or vegetables?

Do you often experience digestive discomfort (e.g. bloating; indigestion)?
Do you consume fermented foods or probiotic supplements regularly?
How often do you consume sugary or high-fat foods?
How often do you experience stress or anxiety?
Do you find it difficult to maintain focus or motivation?
Do you have issues falling asleep?
